After Susan Murphy (voiced by Reese Witherspoon) is 
struck by a meteor and grows to be 50-feet tall, 
she's captured by the government and shuttled to a 
secret compound where she meets a team of other 
monsters -- soon to be Earth's only defense when an 
alien attacks. Under orders from the president 
(Stephen Colbert), Susan and her cohorts Dr. Cockroach 
(Hugh Laurie), the Missing Link (Will Arnett) and B.O.B. 
(Seth Rogen) set out to save the world.

Starring: Seth Rogen, Reese Witherspoon

Director: Rob Letterman
